<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id74c2b005-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 300111 was renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t36/s300113">section 300113 of this title</ref>.</p>
